        <p class="text-white font-semibold mb-2">Explore Tile Combinations</p>
        <p class="text-gray-300 text-sm mb-3">Use our word finder to see every possible word from any set of remaining tiles — perfect for practicing your endgame analysis.</p>
        <a href="/" class="inline-block px-4 py-2 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white text-sm font-medium rounded-lg transition-colors">Try the Word Finder →</a>
      </div>

      <aside class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-12 pt-8 not-prose">
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm font-medium mb-3">Related Articles</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          <li><a href="/blog/reading-your-opponents-rack/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline text-sm">Reading Your Opponent's Rack</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/playing-the-endgame-like-a-pro/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline text-sm">Playing the Endgame Like a Pro</a></li>
          <li><a href="/blog/how-experts-evaluate-a-rack/" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline text-sm">How Experts Evaluate a Rack</a></li>
